title: Tua Tagovailoa, Dak Prescott, NBA, where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Tua Tagovailoa, Dak Prescott, NBA, where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin talks about Tua Tagovailoa being ready for the NFL because of where he played, why he believes Dak Prescott made a mistake over the weekend, why the NBA can get by playing in empty arenas, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Peter King, Trent Dilfer, and Hunter Renfrow,
